.class public auto ansi beforefieldinit Line extends DocumentFormat.OpenXml.TypedOpenXmlCompositeElement

summary.para: Line.
This class is available in Office 2007 and above.
When the object is serialized out as xml, it's qualified name is v:line.

remarks.format:
## Remarks [!INCLUDE[openxmlnoticeiso](~/includes/openxmlnoticeiso.md)]
`line (Line)`
This element draws a straight line.
[*Example*:
```xml <v:line from="10pt,10pt" to="75pt,35pt" strokecolor="blue" strokeweight="3pt"> </v:line> ```
